	JMS GETNUM	/RECEIVE CDF INSTRUCTION
	DCA CDFSTO
	JMS GETNUM	/RECEIVE NEGATIVE WORD COUNT
	DCA WORDCT
GETACK,	JMS GETNUM	/4000=READ, 4001=WRITE, 0000=DONE, 2000=ERROR
	SNA		/WAS IT ZERO?
